text: Liandala Sena Fanai (born 21 November 1993) is an Indian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Minerva Punjab in the I-League. ==Career== Born in Mizoram, Fanai began his career with Bethlehem Vengthalang before moving to George Telegraph of the Calcutta Football League in 2016. He soon joined Chennai City of the I-League and made his professional debut for the side on 31 January 2017.
